SIMPLE: militate_against
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: militate against
<hw>mil"i*tate a*gainst"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To
argue against; to cast doubt on; -- used in reference to facts which
tend to disprove a hypothesis; <as>as, the absence of a correlation of
budget deficits with inflation <ex>militates against</ex> any causal
relation between the two</as>. Opposite of
<contr>support</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Militia</ent>⟦br⟧
